CITIER (Class Inheritance & Table Inheritance Embeddings for Rails) is a solution for single and multiple class table inheritance.
It is based on code by ALTRABio (www.github.com/altrabio/) and built upon/fixed/cleaned and evolved into to CITIER for my own (And potentially other's) needs

For full information: http://peterejhamilton.github.com/citier/
For the original version by ALTRABio see www.github.com/altrabio/